@startuml
title Track Ticket Status - Activity Diagram

start

:Enter Ticket ID;
note right
Student enters the ticket ID in the Ticket Status UI.
end note

:Display Progress;
note right
System shows ticket status lookup progress or processing status
to the student.
end note

:Send Status Request;
note right
Ticket Status UI sends getStatus(ticketId)
to TicketStatusController.
end note

:Retrieve Current Status;
note right
TicketStatusController retrieves the current status
from MaintenanceTicket.
end note

:Load Status History / Updates;
note right
TicketStatusController loads status history and updates
from StatusHistory.
end note

:Return Status + History;
note right
System returns the current ticket status and status history
to the Ticket Status UI.
end note

if (New Status Update Event Received?) then (Yes)
  :Process Notification Event;
  note right
  Notification API / service forwards a status update event
  and the controller refreshes the latest ticket status.
  end note
else (No)
endif

:Show Ticket Status;
note right
Ticket Status UI displays the current status and history timeline
to the student.
end note

stop
@enduml
